publisher			Matt Makes Games Inc.							
publish_time	 2014年3月11日		
desc_long							评测						“The new gold standard in the local multiplayer renaissance”9.5 / 10 – Polygon“Aggressively focused, humbly spectacular, and nearly unimpeachable in its design”10 / 10 – EGM“Destined to be remembered as one of the best multiplayer games of all time”CVG												关于这款游戏							TowerFall Ascension is the definitive version of the hit archery combat game. Inspired by classics from the golden age of couch multiplayer, it's a 4-player local party game centering around hilarious, intense versus matches. The core mechanics are simple and accessible, but hard to master and combat is fierce. Loot treasure chests for game-changing power-ups, master the art of catching arrows out of the air, or descend on your foes and stomp them into submission. TowerFall is best played competitively with friends, cross-legged on the floor within punching distance of each other.New in Ascension is the 1- or 2-player co-op Quest mode. Players work together, fighting off a variety of monsters and enemy archers across the land of TowerFall. It's a new adventure to explore when you don't have more friends handy to square off against.New features in TowerFall Ascension include:Brand new 1- or 2-player co-op Quest mode50 additional Versus arenas, for a total of 120 unique mapsMore game-changing power-ups, such as Drill Arrows that burrow through walls4 new unlockable, playable archers, for a total of 8A huge list of variants to customize your matches - a total of 75 ways to mix things upPlenty of hidden secrets and surprises to discover with your friends						
